pan></div><p class=\"mt-4 flex-1 font-lato text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-800 line-clamp-4\">“<!-- -->Mardi Himal is an off-the-beaten-path gem. Less crowded than Poon Hill but equally stunning. Our guide was excellent — knew every bird and plant along the trail. Only reason for 4 stars instead of 5 is the teahouse at High Camp was a little basic.<!-- -->”</p><button class=\"mt-2 self-start font-montserrat text-xs font-semibold text-green-600 hover:text-amber-600\">Read more</button><div class=\"mt-5 flex items-center justify-between border-t border-stone-200 pt-4\"><span class=\"font-montserrat text-xs text-stone-500\">December 2023</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-montserrat text-xs font-semibold text-green-600\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-4 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-600 text-snow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" width=\"11\" height=\"11\"><path d=\"m5 12 4.5 4.5L19 7\"></path></svg></span>Verified Trek</span></div></article><article class=\"flex h-full flex-col rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 bg-warm p-6 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-amber-400/60 hover:shadow-trek\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-700 font-montserrat text-sm font-bold text-snow\">DO</div><div class=\"min-w-0\"><p class=\"truncate font-dm text-lg leading-tight text-green-900\">David Okafor</p><p class=\"font-montserrat text-xs text-stone-500\">🇳🇬<!-- --> <!-- -->Nigeria</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-4 flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 \"><div class=\"flex\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><button type=\"button\" disabled=\"\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 cursor-default\" aria-label=\"1 star\"><svg view